Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.74,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My first time switching schools...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.70,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad decided to open a \Nstudio in the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.19,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,so we left Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.51,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,and I changed schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:37.18,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be okay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:40.56,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,in my new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:18.97,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,1)}Episode 12\N"Fireworks\N(Once Again)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:56.63,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.36,Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.08,Main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.48,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:04.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.58,Hinode-hama Port Station,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hinode-hama Port Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Touko Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kakeru Okikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.00,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.12,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.27,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for the fireworks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:35.48,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Not too many are around yet, \Nbut there'll be more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fireworks festival today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:40.68,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.89,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:46.12,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a beach and a pier \Nto the right of that harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.12,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the stage for the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.13,Cafe,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Café Kazemichi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.14,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's snowed in\N and stuck in his tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.95,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,He's still living in his tent? In this snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.21,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If Sacchan says no, then no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.03,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your hot orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Touko Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to introduce yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hiro Shirosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.93,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Yanagi Takayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.85,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukinari Imi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.14,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that? Yuki was\Njust staring at Fukami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinari falls in love with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.56,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my job to show her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.28,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,around Hinode-hama today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.43,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.74,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sachi Nagamiya.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:19.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My father is opening a studio here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.45,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,A studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:24.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he makes art glass \Nand vases and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.48,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a lot more hot and \Ntedious than you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for the fireworks, right? \NThe fireworks here are pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.27,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she didn't know \Nabout the fireworks today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.06,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.62,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,We all get together every \Nyear to watch the fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.95,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,from a place called Hinode-hama Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.62,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time now. \NAll the way from elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:56.37,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's been like that\Never since we set up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.48,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,a weird new rule when we were younger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.13,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,that we always had to \Nbe in groups of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:06.33,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that ends up happening \Nwithout anyone really talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.93,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You should come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be twice as fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.22,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Right, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.18,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.71,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.97,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not used to the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I grew up where there's no snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.65,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Try to keep your center of gravity \Nstraight above your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.37,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,and walk in small steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:39.84,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You can see all of Hinode-hama from \Nthe deck on the fourth floor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.98,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really hear about \Nfireworks in the winter, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wonder what fireworks \Nare like in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You probably wouldn't be able \Nto see them anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:11.29,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is looking forward\N to going with you, too, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.80,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, are you going to Hinode-hama \NHigh School for your third year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.00,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hope to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Must be tough transferring \Nin your third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm want to go to art school, so it's probably \Nmore about practice than studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.31,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.25,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking over for your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.00,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:44.57,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been outside this \Ntown, so I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.60,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What's it like being in a new town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.95,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the city more \Nbefore the fireworks start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.11,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.95,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll try walking by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big town, and everyone's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.22,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a new girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to knock anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.06,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,but when you're coming up to a boy's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.69,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,can you at least put out a\Nvibe that you're approaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.06,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?" Because it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.99,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So how was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's passable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.33,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can beat the tragic \Nglasses girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, if you have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.51,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.45,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Tee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it just \Nbecause you seem okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.63,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. It'd be a shame if I got injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.94,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.37,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Twelve more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.24,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.37,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your routine is important to you. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.71,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.36,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.25,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.37,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,So cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:07.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping him? He should be \Non his shorter route today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.75,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.87,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:53.84,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the fireworks \Nwith everyone, like always?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:59.38,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be watching from the rooftop as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.93,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We've invited the Fukami-san family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.97,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Fukami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.68,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They have daughters in high \Nschool and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.00,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I mention?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They're opening a glassware studio nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.13,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.65,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out they're in my fan club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I have plans to meet up with the older \Ngirl at Hinode-hama Shrine later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.20,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.50,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It just kinda happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.54,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be really crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.12,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's her first time in Hinode-hama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.25,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.97,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I guess I should go pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.76,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like they're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.96,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She called me on her cell \Nphone before we got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.94,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,and she said she wanted \Nto look around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.53,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need Touko's cell phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.32,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan moves fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.42,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I know, in a blink of an eye. \NI wonder who she got that from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.66,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.96,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:06.87,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.25,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.77,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I don't have my phone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.01,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.35,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.88,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at the neighborhood association.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.91,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Don't be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.84,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:50.55,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, please take care of Sachi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.73,Italics,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, that idiot. It's already starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.84,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't take off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.30,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:28.93,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.40,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.91,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.54,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What, they don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.77,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But we just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.56,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are they acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.84,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.94,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are they serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.88,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They seriously don't recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.59,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.62,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.97,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Weird girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:01.67,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.17,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I bet you wanted \Nto go with Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:15.46,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I don't like crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.41,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.73,Italics,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Onee-chan's making the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.91,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:33.20,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You know some pretty old cheers, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty awesome this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.26,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.51,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:38.98,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.91,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried. You wouldn't \Npick up your phone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone else here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.36,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.22,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks are starting already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.96,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.55,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to watch from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.69,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they waiting at the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.50,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be nice for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like we'll be able \Nto make it to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.14,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We'll make do \Nby ourselves this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:05.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Variety is the, uh, what was it—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.22,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,Spice of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.12,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Another spice of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.33,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.25,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see, too, Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.65,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.68,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that counts as \Nan indirect kiss, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:46.82,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Indirect what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:47.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the world of my \Nfragments of the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:59.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Kakeru-kun that I imagined?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.28,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm different \Nagain from my earlier self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You could say I'm a projection of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.90,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,myself from your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:11.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} Kakeru-kun \Nfrom my imaginary world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.20,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.37,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So what about Yana-chan and \Nthe others, over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,They're not real either,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.14,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,in a different sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.01,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They're not real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:27.32,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,They might have had some reasons \Nthat they couldn't get together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.74,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.56,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm definitely real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And my loneliness earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:51.26,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,During the fireworks show,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.08,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be seen by the Yana-chan and Sacchan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.62,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,and Hiro-kun and Yuki-kun of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:01.18,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have an unforgettable place
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.99,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,where I spent time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.33,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.30,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.21,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.06,Main,Sacchan,0000,0000,0000,,I like the name "Touko."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:35.43,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.55,Main,Yukinari,0000,0000,0000,,It changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:37.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:40.89,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,1)}Final Episode\N"Shooting Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
